Description: Autonomous AI assistant runtime
 Human is a lightweight, self-contained AI assistant runtime written in C.
 Features include 50+ AI providers, 33 messaging channels, 66+ tools,
 vector memory, sandboxing, MCP support, and a web dashboard.
